column5: Jadens got Monday off so we grabbed her and a friend (Nat) and headed up to camp!  Water is still high which makes the fishing harder, and boy oh boy are the mosquitoes AND blackflies out in force!!  heres some pics  Critters everywhere..    Camp at Night!!      Nat and Jaden                Back home for a few days tomorrow, then off to Kesagami!!  Woot!
Nice, now draw up a sign already!
Christmas light in June!  Good times boss.
Great stuff.  Love the sunset pics.  Great heart shaped glasses on Nat!
Great shots and guality family time
Awesome boss !!!! Looks like everything is great kids are on fish !!! Scenery is stunning  first get much better than that !!!!! Cheers
Nice TJ, and good luck at Kesagami.  If you guys don't have a screen tent for sitting outside in the evening you should get one.
More fish in this post than when you and Monique are fishing......
